    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BitRick’s Venture is a fast-paced roguelite shooter with procedural map generation where you control BitRick, a guy with a questionable sense of humor who loves trash-talking after humiliating his enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of survivor-like games where a run takes half an hour to end? Welcome. Here, you will die in under 8 minutes. But hey, look on the bright side… at least you can earn some cool hats while learning how to actually play!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you make it through all the floors?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple floors infested with horrifying creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random events that only help if you are really lucky.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sinister bosses that will beat you up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 items to aid you on your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 30 cosmetics to unlock. Do they boost stats? No. But they will make you look awesome.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267530/extras/b79b58075a83b8a9e7d88fe58dae9068.poster.avif?t=1767643968\" width=768 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267530/extras/b79b58075a83b8a9e7d88fe58dae9068.webm?t=1767643968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267530/extras/b79b58075a83b8a9e7d88fe58dae9068.mp4?t=1767643968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
